title: Microsoft Office 2013 VL ProPlus Visio Project en-US x64 03/2016
description:
Microsoft Office 2013 VL ProPlus Visio Project en-US 64-bit March 2016

Release Info

File versions
Office 2013: 15.0.4454.1000
Visio Pro: 15.0.4569.1506
Project Pro: 15.0.4569.1506

Includes

- Microsoft Office Professional Plus (x64 Volume License en-US) / Project Pro / Visio Pro
- Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (activator)
- Visual Studio for Office Runtime (version 10.0.60724), required update
- Optional: Classic Menu for Office v5.85, Office Tab v9.81, Remove Sign In icon Office 2013 (reg file)

Source files:

- Office ProPlus 2013: SW_DVD5_Office_Professional_Plus_2013w_SP1_64Bit_English_MLF_X19-35976.ISO
- Project Pro 2013: SW_DVD5_Project_Pro_2013w_SP1_64Bit_English_MLF_X19-35816.ISO
- Visio Pro 2013: SW_DVD5_Visio_Pro_2013w_SP1_64Bit_English_MLF_X19-36393.ISO

Integrated updates

March 08, 2016

Installation

- Install Office 2013
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (add-ins folder, click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button)
- Install Visual Studio for Office Runtime (add-ins folder)
- Install any of these optional utilities (add-ins folder)

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 + serial
- Office Tab v9.81 + serial
- Merge reg file 'Remove Sign In icon Office 2013' to remove the "Sign in" option

System requirements

64-bit version of Windows 10/8.1/8,7 SP1 + Server/Server 2012 R2/2012/Server 2008 R2

Please SEED for a while!
